---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Get Involved" description="Learn how to participate in LABAC and make a difference for cycling in Los Angeles.">
  <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
    There are many ways to participate in LABAC and help improve cycling in Los Angeles.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Attend a Meeting</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    All LABAC meetings are open to the public. Meetings are held on the first Tuesday of every even-numbered month at 7:00 PM at City Hall. Check the <a href="/meetings" class="text-primary hover:underline">meeting schedule</a> for details.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Submit Public Comment</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Each meeting includes a public comment period where community members can address the committee. You can also submit written comments in advance.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Request an Agenda Item</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    Have a topic you'd like the committee to discuss? Contact us to request that an item be added to an upcoming meeting agenda.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Apply to Join the Committee</h2>
  <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
    LABAC members are appointed by City Council members. If you're interested in serving, contact your council representative to express interest when a vacancy occurs.
  </p>
</PageLayout>
